claim: Vikrant Massey acted in V The Serial.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He is noted for his leading roles in TV series , Dharam Veer  (  2008  )  , Balika Vadhu  (  2009  )  , Baba Aiso Varr Dhoondo  (  2010  )  , V The Serial  (  2012  )  and Qubool Hai  (  2013  )  and in Bollywood movies Lootera and Dil Dhadakne Do .
